2pt</PaddingRight><PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop><PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom></Style></Textbox><Textbox Name="Textbox82"><CanGrow>true</CanGrow><KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>The Certificate Holder will have the priority enrolment right in the enrolment year as stated in the Certificate at the UEF Collaborative Bachelors’ Programme with the University of Gloucestershire or  Leeds  Trinity  University  (“  University  ”)  where the UEF and the  Dai-ichi  Life  Cambodia agree to reserve the place for priority enrolment at the time of the purchase of the Educational Insurance Product, provided that the following conditions are satisfied:</Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>9pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Left</TextAlign><LineHeight>12pt</LineHeight></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><rd:DefaultName>Textbox81</rd:DefaultName><Top>11.45832in</Top><Left>0.22in</Left><Height>0.52778in</Height><Width>10.92527in</Width><ZIndex>39</ZIndex><Style><Border><Color>White</Color><Style>None</Style></Border><VerticalAlign>Top</VerticalAlign><PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop><PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom></Style></Textbox><Textbox Name="Textbox84"><CanGrow>true</CanGrow><KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>a.</Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>9pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Right</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>b.</Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>9pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Right</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><rd:DefaultName>Textbox84</rd:DefaultName><Top>11.9861in</Top><Left>0.22in</Left><Height>0.37in</Height><Width>0.35in</Width><ZIndex>40</ZIndex><Style><Border><Color>White</Color><Style>None</Style></Border><TopBorder><Width>1pt</Width></TopBorder><BottomBorder><Width>1pt</Width></BottomBorder><LeftBorder><Width>1pt</Width></LeftBorder><RightBorder><Width>1pt</Width></RightBorder><VerticalAlign>Top</VerticalAlign><PaddingLeft>2pt</PaddingLeft><PaddingRight>2pt</PaddingRight><PaddingTop>2pt</PaddingTop><PaddingBottom>2pt</PaddingBottom></Style></Textbox><Textbox Name="Textbox173"><CanGrow>true</CanGrow><KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether><Paragraphs><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>The Insurance Policy on which the Certificate depends must be still in force at the time of enrolment and its due premiums have been fully paid.</Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>9pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Left</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph><Paragraph><TextRuns><TextRun><Value>The Customer shall select one course,  which the  Certificate  Holder  will apply,  to enter and shall give a notice to the  UEF  about the name of the course,  at least one  (1)  year prior to the enrolment.</Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontSize>9pt</FontSize><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun><TextRun><Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value><Style><FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle><FontFamily>Arial</FontFamily><FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight><TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration></Style></TextRun></TextRuns><Style><TextAlign>Left</TextAlign></Style></Paragraph></Paragraphs><rd:DefaultN